quran[44]{c,v,t}:
  38,52,Hamwe nabo bazoba ho n’abanega babo bahumurije amaso yabo kubatambukanyi babo
  38,53,Ibi nivyo mwaraganiwe k’umusi w’imperuka
  38,54,Mu vy’ukuri iyi niyo migisha yacu idahera
  38,55,Nuko rero mu vy’ukuri bamwe barenga imbibe ingaruka zabo zizoba ziri ahantu habi cane
  38,56,Wamuriro witiriwe Jahannamu niwo bazokwinjiramwo naho nahateguwe nabi cane
  38,57,N’uku bizoba rero nibahonje amazi y’amarike n’amashira
  38,58,N’ibindi bihano nk’ibi ni vyinshi
  38,59,"Izi nizo ngabo zizo kwinjira hamwe namwe, mugabo ntizaronse ahantu heza zishikira mugabo zizo kwinjira mu muriro udahera"
  38,60,"Bavuze bati:- mwebwe ntakaze ryiza mufise mwebwe nimwe mwatumye turonka ibihano aho naho n’ahantu h’ubwicaro bubi cane"
  38,61,"Bavuze bati:- Muremyi wacu, abatumye tugira ibi vyose, n’ubongereze ibihano vy’incuro zibiri iyo mu muriro udahera"
  38,62,"Bazovuga\tbati:-\tvyabaye\tgute\tko\ttutababona\tbabantu\ttwahora tubaharura ko bari mu bantu babi"
  38,63,Erega twaraba kengereye mugabo amaso yacu ntiyababona gusa
  38,64,Ntankeka ibi bintu vy’amatati y’abantu bo mumuriro udahera nay’ukuri
  38,65,"Vuga\tuti:-\tmu\tvy’ukuri\tjewe\tnd’uwutuza\tgusa,\tkandi\tntayindi\tMana itegerezwa gusengwa atariyo yonyene rudende nyene ubushobozi"
  38,66,Umumenyi w’Amajuru n’Isi hamwe nibirimwo vyose nyene ubushobozi hamwe n’ikigongwe cinshi
  38,67,"Vuga uti:- izi n’inkuru zihambaye cane"
  38,68,Mutitayeho namba
  38,69,Ntabumenyi nari mfise bw’ibiremwa bitagatifu mugihe batumvikana
  38,70,Simbwirwa ikintu na kimwe kuri jewe atari uko nd’umuntu atuza abantu kandi mboneka
  38,71,"Umuremyi wawe mugihe yababwira Abamarayika ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nzorema umuntu ndamukuye mw’ivu"
  38,72,"Ninarangiza kurema uyo muntu nukumu huhera umutima uvuye\tkuri jewe, rero nimuce mumupfukamira nukumu gamburukira"
  38,73,Bara gamburutse Abamarayika bose uko bangana bose
  38,74,Dukuyemwo uwitwa Ibilisi yishimye nukuba muba hakanyi b’Imana
  38,75,"Imana yamubwiye iti:- ewe Ibilisi, n’igiki cakubujje ku gamburukira uwo naremye ku maboko yanje, mbega winamuye canke wabaye mubantu bakuru"
  38,76,"Nawe yishura ati:- jewe ndimwiza gusumba uyo waremye, kuko jewe wandemye unkuye mu muriro udahera, nawe umurema umukuye mw’ivu"
  38,77,"Imana\tica\tivuga\titi:-\tnuve\tmuri\tuwo\tmuriro\tudahera\tkuko\turamaze gutabwa kure n’imigisha yanje"
  38,78,Mu vy’ukuri umuvumo wanje uzoba hejuru yawe kuri kugeza k’umusi w’imperuka
  38,79,"Nawe yishura ati:- Muremyi wanje, numpe umwanya na mutoyi gusa kugeza k’umusi bazozurwa ibiremwa vyose"
  38,80,"Imana imubwira iti:- nivyo wewe uri mubaronse ikibanza c’ukubaho"
  38,81,Kugeza kumwanya w’umusi wategekanijwe
  38,82,"Nawe yishura ati:- ndarahiye k’ukuri kw’iteka ryawe ntankeka jewe abo bantu bawe nzobazimiza uko bangana bose"
  38,83,Dukuye mwo ba bantu bawe muribo ar’intore
  38,84,"Imana ivuga iti:- ndarahiye mvugishije ukuri"
  38,85,Mu vy’ukuri jewe nzokwuzuza mu muriro udahera kuri wewe Shetani hamwe n’abagu kurikira muribo
  38,86,"Vuga uti:- jewe sindaba saba impembo kuri ibi, kandi jewe sindi mu bantu bitegeka"
  38,87,Ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko ari ubutumwa ku bantu bose
  38,88,Kandi ntankeka mwebwe muzomenya inkuru ziwe mumwanya
  39,1,Imanuka ry’iki gitabu gitagatifu nikivuye ku Mana nyene ubushobozi hamwe n’ubuhizi buhagije
  39,2,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twaku manuriye iki gitabu bimwe vy’ukuri, rero n’usenge Imana yawe nukuyigira yuko ariyo Muremyi wenyene gusa"
  39,3,"Uwizerwa w’Umuremyi n’Imana yonyene gusa, mugabo bamwe bagira abandi kuba arizo Mana aho kuba ariyo yonyene rudende bavuga bati:- twebwe abo ntituba senga mugabo niba dushikane hafi cane y’Imana, mu vy’ukuri Imana izocira urubanza ruri hagati yabo kuvyo batumvikanye ko, ntankeka Imana ntirongora umubeshi w’umuhakanyi w’Imana"
  39,4,"Iyo Imana ibishaka ngo ironke ikibondo ntankeka yari gutora uwo yishakiye mubo yiremeye, mugabo iri kure yivyo vyose kuko n’Imana imwe yonyene rudende igira ivyo yishakiye"
  39,5,"Niyo yaremye Amajuru n’Isi bimwe vy’ukuri, ikaba ariyo yapfuse Ijoro hejuru y’Umutaga kandi ikaba ariyo yapfuse Umutaga hejuru y’Ijoro kandi ikaba ariyo yagamburukije Izuba n’Ukwezi vyose bikagira gusa kugihe categekanijwe, mumenye yuko ariyo nyene ubushobozi kandi ariyo nyene ikigongwe cinshi"
  39,6,"Niyo yabaremye mu mutima umwe, hanyuma igira mugenziwe kuba nkawe nukuba manurira ibikoko umunani harimwo impfizi n’inyana, rero ibarema munda z’abavyeyi banyu mufise iremwa ritandukanye n’irindi, riri mumyijima itatu, iyo rero niyo Mana ariyo Muremyi wanyu, ubwami bwose ni rwiwe kandi ntawundi asengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atariyo yonyene gusa, none mwebwe muhindukizwa hehe"
  39,7,"Ni mwaba muri ahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, Imana ntibakeneye mwebwe mugabo ntiyemera ubuhakanyi bw’abantu bayo beranda, rero nimwa shima ivyo nivyo biyinezereza kuko biba bivuye kuri mwebwe, n’uwikorera ntazo kwikorera itu ry’uwundi, hanyuma ingaruka yanyu niku Muremyi wanyu, niyo izoba bwira ivyo mwahora mugira, ntankeka niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibiri mubikiriza vyanyu"